16
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:13,330
Father.

17
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,600
Father.

18
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:39,530
These victims had all been wearing

19
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,030
clothing,

20
00:02:42,090 --> 00:02:43,430
Am I dreaming?

21
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:44,700
accessories,

