00:23:22,140 --> 00:23:23,270
for interrogation.

597
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:25,360
However, he refuses to admit that

598
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:26,310
he was involved

599
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:27,840
in the Qi Vital Stone trade.

600
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,840
Not even I could get it out of him.

601
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:31,650
If he refuses to confess

602
00:23:31,650 --> 00:23:32,900
even to Your Highness,

603
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:34,380
it means the person

604
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,820
behind the Qi Vital Stone trade

605
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:36,820
is very powerful.

606
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:38,580
I'll keep investigating.

607
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:42,080
I've demoted Eunuch Li to the Laundry Service

608
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,540
for attempted assault,

609
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:46,910
to take accountability for what he did to you.

610
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,760
Thank you, Your Highness.

611
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:51,660
Captured.

612
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:54,540
Your move

613
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:57,020
is too hasty.

614
00:23:58,180 --> 00:23:58,700
Really?

615
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:03,180
I won.

616
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:05,840
You...

617
00:24:07,380 --> 00:24:07,950
When did you

618
00:24:07,950 --> 00:24:09,210
come up with this move?

619
00:24:09,660 --> 00:24:10,990
Everything has been going according to my plan

620
00:24:10,990 --> 00:24:12,920
since the beginning of this match.

621
00:24:12,980 --> 00:24:15,570
This move is called "the rat crosses the river from the left

622
00:24:15,570 --> 00:24:16,660
to kill the tiger and depose the elephant."

623
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:17,590
Amazing, right?

624
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:19,920
What strategy is this?

625
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:21,280
I've never heard of it.

626
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:25,590
An old friend of mine

627
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,470
came up with it.

628
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:29,110
He taught me secretly.

629
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:32,990
I'm curious.

630
00:24:33,860 --> 00:24:34,980
Hundred Beast Chess

631
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,540
is only popular in Qi.

632
00:24:36,700 --> 00:24:37,830
How did you learn it?

633
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,300
You play so well, too.

634
00:24:40,020 --> 00:24:40,880
A few years ago,

635
00:24:41,370 --> 00:24:42,830
a courtier gifted me a set.

636
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:48,100
My wife liked it very much.

637
00:24:48,610 --> 00:24:49,940
I often played with her.

638
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:52,300
I've heard about

639
00:24:52,330 --> 00:24:53,900
what had happened to the Crown Princess.

640
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:55,500
She must have been

641
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:56,910
a very unique woman.

642
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:00,980
In my heart,

643
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:03,710
she has no equal.

644
00:25:09,290 --> 00:25:10,720
I've never even

645
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:11,610
shown

646
00:25:11,820 --> 00:25:12,700
Han Zheng

647
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:13,380
this move.

648
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:15,700
I've taught Your Highness today.

649
00:25:18,330 --> 00:25:19,680
Speaking of Prince Han,

650
00:25:20,300 --> 00:25:21,060
I think

651
00:25:21,570 --> 00:25:22,530
you can't wait

652
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:24,050
to get down to business.

653
00:25:26,390 --> 00:25:28,120
I'll get straight to the point.

654
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:30,400
What will happen to Han Zheng?

655
00:25:31,090 --> 00:25:33,350
He killed a Senior Inspector by mistake.

656
00:25:33,730 --> 00:25:34,660
After the trial,

657
00:25:34,860 --> 00:25:36,060
if he's found guilty,

658
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,190
according to the legal code of the Qian,

659
00:25:37,190 --> 00:25:38,140
he'll probably be sentenced

660
00:25:38,140 --> 00:25:39,340
to 20 years in prison.

661
00:25:43,330 --> 00:25:44,860
But there's one good thing.

662
00:25:45,010 --> 00:25:46,470
Given the lifespan of a Qi,

663
00:25:46,740 --> 00:25:47,600
20 years later,

664
00:25:49,980 --> 00:25:52,180
Prince Han should still be in his prime.

665
00:25:53,970 --> 00:25:54,830
Your Highness.

666
00:25:55,450 --> 00:25:56,780
Are you making fun of us?

667
00:25:58,390 --> 00:25:59,390
I'm just kidding.

668
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:02,450
Since Han Zheng is a Qi,

669
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:03,880
even if he must be imprisoned,

670
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:04,510
it should be

671
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:05,760
in a Qi prison.

672
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:07,210
What do you think?

673
00:26:09,530 --> 00:26:10,330
In my opinion,

674
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,840
allowing Han Zheng to return to Qi

675
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:14,770
will be to set a dangerous man free.

676
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:15,500
I'm afraid

677
00:26:16,060 --> 00:26:18,920
he won't even have to walk through the prison doors.

678
00:26:19,730 --> 00:26:20,760
That's not true.

679
00:26:22,620 --> 00:26:23,450
You can send someone

680
00:26:23,450 --> 00:26:24,910
to check on him regularly.

681
00:26:25,870 --> 00:26:26,940
You can just send him to prison

682
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:27,740
once in a while

683
00:26:28,010 --> 00:26:28,810
as a pretense.

684
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:34,480
Your Highness.

685
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,850
I'll be frank with you.

686
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,660
If Han Zheng is really found guilty

687
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:39,660
of manslaughter,

688
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:40,830
he will be punished.

689
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,500
In exchange for bringing him back

690
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:44,630
to be punished in Qi,

691
00:26:44,700 --> 00:26:45,800
I will agree to any demand you make,

692
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:48,460
with the exception of the Qian-Qi Six Treaties.

693
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:51,750
For the next five years,

694
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,580
we can double our tribute

695
00:26:54,150 --> 00:26:55,820
of white camels, horses, gyrfalcons,

696
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:57,750
black gold, Qi knives, and grains.

697
00:26:57,770 --> 00:26:59,170
If I remember correctly,

698
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:01,580
during the beginning of autumn last year,

699
00:27:01,580 --> 00:27:02,260
you captured two

700
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,190
Qian travelers.

701
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:07,450
The men you are calling travelers

702
00:27:07,450 --> 00:27:09,530
were clearly spies.

703
00:27:12,810 --> 00:27:14,540
Besides doubling the tribute,

704
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:16,280
if you let them go,

705
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,830
I'll allow Prince Han to return with you

706
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:20,630
to receive his punishment in Qi.

707
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:22,870
These two spies

708
00:27:22,910 --> 00:27:24,710
have been hiding in Qi for years.

709
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:26,430
They have too much intel.

710
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:28,060
Even if I agree,

711
00:27:28,380 --> 00:27:29,910
the King of Xueqi might not.

712
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:33,780
In that case, I feel sorry

713
00:27:33,780 --> 00:27:34,640
for Prince Han.

714
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:36,390
To the King of Xueqi,

715
00:27:37,050 --> 00:27:37,850
his son's life

716
00:27:38,460 --> 00:27:39,320
cannot compare to the Qian-Qi Six Treaties.

717
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,050
That's fine.

718
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:43,690
But it can't even compare to two spies.

719
00:27:46,020 --> 00:27:47,080
It's settled then.

720
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:48,820
I will persuade His Majesty.

721
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,260
Your Highness,

722
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:52,050
don't break your promise.

723
00:27:52,900 --> 00:27:54,360
I have one more condition.

724
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:55,980
Your Prince Han

725
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:59,070
repeatedly stirred up trouble in Jiuxiao City.

726
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:00,690
This time, especially,

727
00:28:00,890 --> 00:28:02,260
he created grievances amongst the people

728
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:03,190
of Jiuxiao City.

729
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,720
In the future,

730
00:28:04,940 --> 00:28:06,990
he is not allowed to enter Jiuxiao City again.

731
00:28:06,990 --> 00:28:08,220
Only this will appease the anger of the people.

732
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:09,220
What do you think?

733
00:28:09,890 --> 00:28:10,420
Alright.

734
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:11,980
Are you sure

735
00:28:12,940 --> 00:28:15,000
you can make Prince Han agree as well?

736
00:28:15,170 --> 00:28:16,300
I heard from Jun that

737
00:28:16,780 --> 00:28:18,300
he has a close relationship

738
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:19,300
with Miss Jiu'er.

739
00:28:19,710 --> 00:28:22,440
I'm afraid he'll be unwillng to leave her behind.

740
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:24,260
Prince Han seems defiant,

741
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,620
but he knows what his responsibilities are.

742
00:28:26,620 --> 00:28:27,750
On crucial matters,

743
00:28:28,060 --> 00:28:30,190
he knows how to make the right choices.

744
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:31,240
Alright.

745
00:28:33,330 --> 00:28:34,190
Another round?

746
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:48,230
Sending me this far is enough, Your Highness.

747
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:49,470
General Chilan.

748
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:54,350
Please wait.

749
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:55,920
I've prepared a carriage for you.

750
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,050
It'll send you back.

751
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:04,300
There's no need to stand on ceremony, Your Highness.

752
00:29:04,300 --> 00:29:05,450
We Qi

753
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,840
don't need carriages.

754
00:29:07,540 --> 00:29:08,600
It's not ceremony.

755
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:09,780
Consider it

756
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:11,600
my concern for you.

757
00:29:15,010 --> 00:29:16,010
This way, please.

758
00:29:21,620 --> 00:29:22,360
Be careful.

759
00:29:39,170 --> 00:29:41,020
Send someone to escort her along the way.

760
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:41,340
Yes.

761
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:10,590
Captured.

762
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:12,600
Have you decided?

763
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:13,330
Are you sure?

764
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:14,980
What do you mean?

765
00:30:17,870 --> 00:30:18,820
I made a mistake?

766
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,230
Or are you lying to me?

767
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:23,630
Take a guess.

768
00:30:29,810 --> 00:30:30,700
You must be afraid

769
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,620
I'll capture your leopard.

770
00:30:31,620 --> 00:30:32,380
That's why you got riled up.

771
00:30:32,380 --> 00:30:32,980
You're trying to

772
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,240
confuse me on purpose.

773
00:30:36,530 --> 00:30:37,730
I'm making this move.

774
00:30:40,860 --> 00:30:41,500
Forget it.

775
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:43,480
I gave you a chance.

776
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:55,780
When did you

777
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:57,040
come up with this move?

778
00:30:57,470 --> 00:30:58,450
Everything has been going according to my plan

779
00:30:58,450 --> 00:30:59,250
since you made

780
00:30:59,410 --> 00:31:00,840
your first move.

781
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:03,860
This is called "the rat crosses the river from the left

782
00:31:03,860 --> 00:31:06,260
to kill the tiger and depose the elephant."

783
00:31:06,710 --> 00:31:10,900
The rat crosses the river from the left to kill the tiger and depose the elephant.

784
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:12,250
What a silly name.

785
00:31:13,260 --> 00:31:14,460
You're the silly one.

786
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:19,340
Where did you get hurt?

787
00:31:19,340 --> 00:31:20,070
Are you okay?

788
00:31:21,860 --> 00:31:22,590
Does it hurt?

789
00:32:31,380 --> 00:32:31,860
Liu Fu.

790
00:32:32,190 --> 00:32:32,660
Yes.

791
00:32:33,460 --> 00:32:34,870
At what time did I

792
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,960
meet Jiu'er today?

793
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:38,640
A quarter past seven in the morning.

794
00:32:39,490 --> 00:32:41,360
When did I leave Jiu'er?

795
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:45,480
I think it was three quarters past five in the afternoon.

796
00:32:45,610 --> 00:32:48,040
One, two, three, four, five.

797
00:32:49,490 --> 00:32:50,530
I spent 10 hours

798
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,640
with Jiu'er!

799
00:32:52,610 --> 00:32:52,940
Wait.

800
00:32:53,230 --> 00:32:53,940
Your Highness.

801
00:32:53,940 --> 00:32:55,400
Why are you counting this?

802
00:32:55,850 --> 00:32:56,720
Think about it.

803
00:32:57,370 --> 00:32:58,340
Jiu'er only sleeps

804
00:32:58,340 --> 00:32:59,590
for 8 hours every day.

805
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:02,040
That means she only spends 8 hours

806
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:03,730
with Han Zheng in her dream.

807
00:33:04,100 --> 00:33:04,950
In that case,

808
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:05,770
didn't I spend 2 more hours with her

809
00:33:05,770 --> 00:33:07,020
as compared to Han Zheng?

810
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:07,460
Yes.

811
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:07,890
Right?

812
00:33:08,130 --> 00:33:08,770
Tomorrow,

813
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:10,600
let's go even earlier to see Miss Jiu'er.

814
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,180
Yes.

815
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:13,500
Jiu'er has been busy investigating the case lately,

816
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:15,830
so she hasn't had time to think about Brother Han.

817
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:17,170
Gradually,

818
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:19,820
their feelings will fade, right?

819
00:33:20,660 --> 00:33:22,220
Are you hoping Miss Jiu'er

820
00:33:22,380 --> 00:33:24,040
will forget about Prince Han?

821
00:33:24,220 --> 00:33:25,140
But why are you

822
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:26,920
helping him get out of prison?

823
00:33:27,890 --> 00:33:29,210
That's a different matter.

824
00:33:29,210 --> 00:33:30,660
If Brother Han is innocent,

825
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:32,180
I will uphold justice for him.

826
00:33:32,180 --> 00:33:33,750
If Prince Han

827
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,110
is released from prison,

828
00:33:35,110 --> 00:33:36,910
what will you do

829
00:33:37,500 --> 00:33:39,010
if Miss Jiu'er's feelings for him are rekindled?

830
00:33:39,010 --> 00:33:39,870
I'm not afraid.

831
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:42,110
It's absolutely impossible

832
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:44,170
between Brother Han and Miss Jiu'er.

833
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,230
Why?

834
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,580
Like you said,

835
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:47,840
Brother Han

836
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:49,520
is the only son of the King of Xueqi.

837
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:51,650
He has to go back to inherit the throne.

838
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,920
Besides, a Qian and a Qi

839
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,770
cannot have children.

840
00:33:53,770 --> 00:33:54,250
Right?

841
00:33:54,650 --> 00:33:55,160
Yes.

842
00:33:55,190 --> 00:33:57,090
How could the King of Xueqi allow

843
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:58,720
Brother Han to marry Jiu'er?

844
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:00,180
What's wrong, Your Highness?

845
00:34:00,180 --> 00:34:01,620
Help! Help!

846
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:02,560
Wait.

847
00:34:03,110 --> 00:34:05,510
Whenever I mention Brother Han marrying Jiu'er,

848
00:34:05,510 --> 00:34:06,800
my heart aches.

849
00:34:07,690 --> 00:34:08,730
I'm going to bed.

850
00:34:10,889 --> 00:34:12,989
I'll take my leave.

851
00:34:13,719 --> 00:34:15,380
Brother Han marrying Jiu'er.

852
00:34:16,210 --> 00:34:18,170
Brother Han must not marry Jiu'er.

853
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,000
Take your hand away.

854
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,280
Brother Han?

855
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,030
It's me.

856
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:38,270
It's really you?

857
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,219
Aren't you...

858
00:34:40,219 --> 00:34:41,179
Aren't you in prison?

859
00:34:41,179 --> 00:34:42,239
How did you get out?

860
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:43,909
Didn't you let me out?

861
00:34:44,770 --> 00:34:45,969
How is that possible?

862
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,219
That is a crime.

863
00:34:47,219 --> 00:34:48,139
Don't frame me.

864
00:34:49,260 --> 00:34:50,389
I know it wasn't you.

865
00:34:50,739 --> 00:34:51,260
You

866
00:34:51,790 --> 00:34:52,760
would love for me to

867
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:54,260
remain locked up in that prison.

868
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:55,190
That's not true.

869
00:34:55,659 --> 00:34:57,090
I just told Liu Fu about

870
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,860
how to clear your name.

871
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:00,050
If you had come earlier,

872
00:35:00,050 --> 00:35:01,380
you would have heard it.

873
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,550
Come earlier?

874
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:04,020
I have been waiting at your door

875
00:35:04,020 --> 00:35:05,060
since an hour ago.

876
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:12,740
Even if it's impossible between Jiu'er and me,

877
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:14,420
do you stand a chance?

878
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:16,870
Aren't you a prince too?

879
00:35:20,410 --> 00:35:21,750
I'm also a prince.

880
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:24,590
But I have a brother!

881
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:26,300
I don't have to inherit the throne.

882
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:26,830
Besides,

883
00:35:27,410 --> 00:35:28,320
my mother has agreed

884
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,580
to me marrying Jiu'er.

885
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,060
So what if your mother has agreed?

886
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:31,860
Jiu'er won't.

887
00:35:34,180 --> 00:35:35,180
There's no rush.

888
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,940
After you return to Qi

889
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:39,280
and inherit the throne,

890
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,270
I'll spend time with Jiu'er.

891
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:43,830
One day, I will get through to her.

892
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:51,990
Brother Han.

893
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,220
How did you get out?

894
00:35:53,220 --> 00:35:54,010
The agarwood in the prison

895
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:55,260
has already blocked your five senses.

896
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:55,990
I don't know.

897
00:35:57,350 --> 00:35:58,790
A fog suddenly appeared

898
00:35:59,260 --> 00:35:59,920
and the guards

899
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,650
fainted.

900
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:02,940
My door was opened,

901
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:04,110
so I came out.

902
00:36:05,970 --> 00:36:07,990
Someone opened the door for you?

903
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,080
Could it have been Jiu'er?

904
00:36:11,820 --> 00:36:12,550
Impossible.

905
00:36:13,580 --> 00:36:14,360
Even if we don't consider the fact that

906
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,760
Jiu'er still resents me,

907
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:17,700
the person who saved me

908
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:19,460
wore black clothes

909
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:21,370
and deliberately used agarwood

910
00:36:21,370 --> 00:36:22,720
to mask their scent.

911
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:24,320
Jiu'er

912
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:25,350
has no need

913
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:26,490
to go to all that trouble

914
00:36:26,490 --> 00:36:28,090
to hide her identity from me.

915
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,490
Who could it be?

916
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:31,870
I don't know.

917
00:36:32,790 --> 00:36:34,670
No matter what, it must be a trap.

918
00:36:35,530 --> 00:36:36,890
Why did you come out if it was a trap?

919
00:36:36,890 --> 00:36:38,350
I have to fall into his trap

920
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:40,440
to find out what he's after.

921
00:36:47,540 --> 00:36:49,210
No wonder girls don't like you.

922
00:36:49,210 --> 00:36:50,140
You're so petty.

923
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:51,230
I'm going to bed.

924
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:00,640
What?

925
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,260
Han Zheng is gone?

926
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:03,260
Stop pretending.

927
00:37:03,700 --> 00:37:05,460
Exactly. Why are you playing innocent?

928
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:07,620
Tell us the truth. Where did you hide him?

929
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:08,260
Me?

930
00:37:09,460 --> 00:37:09,900
I...

931
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:10,780
Jiu'er.

932
00:37:11,220 --> 00:37:12,000
If it really was you

933
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,260
who released Prince Han,

934
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:14,120
send him back in

935
00:37:14,130 --> 00:37:14,820
right away,

936
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:16,750
before things get out of hand.

937
00:37:16,750 --> 00:37:17,190
Yes.

938
00:37:17,370 --> 00:37:18,080
That's right.

939
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,790
If this gets to the Law Department,

940
00:37:19,790 --> 00:37:20,790
it'll be serious.

941
00:37:21,470 --> 00:37:22,640
Why do you all have to

942
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:23,680
blame it on me?

943
00:37:28,930 --> 00:37:29,680
Listen.

944
00:37:29,710 --> 00:37:30,910
What are they saying?

945
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,290
They said

946
00:37:34,670 --> 00:37:36,330
it was Jiu'er who released me.

947
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:38,390
I knew it.

948
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:39,410
And?

949
00:37:39,640 --> 00:37:41,100
What else are they saying?

950
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:44,540
There are no signs of a struggle

951
00:37:44,540 --> 00:37:45,690
in the cell, right?

952
00:37:46,080 --> 00:37:46,740
The door of the cell

953
00:37:46,740 --> 00:37:48,140
was opened with the key.

954
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,720
Even a fool would know that

955
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:50,430
this was done

956
00:37:50,430 --> 00:37:51,140
by someone from the Inspection Bureau.

957
00:37:51,140 --> 00:37:52,060
That's right.

958
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:53,430
You have the closest relationship

959
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:54,560
with Prince Han.

960
00:37:55,530 --> 00:37:57,140
I can't think of

961
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:58,110
anyone else

962
00:37:58,140 --> 00:37:58,920
who would set him free.

963
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,920
Exactly.

964
00:38:00,340 --> 00:38:01,200
It makes sense.

965
00:38:02,090 --> 00:38:03,410
What do you mean?

966
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:05,140
I've always been

967
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:06,400
the closest to Jiu'er.

968
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:08,110
Doesn't it make sense

969
00:38:08,110 --> 00:38:09,930
that they would suspect it was Jiu'er

970
00:38:09,930 --> 00:38:10,950
who released me?

971
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,840
How does that make sense?

972
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:15,880
She has already cut ties with you.

973
00:38:16,890 --> 00:38:18,490
Can you understand Qian writing?

974
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:19,060
Seriously.

975
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:20,090
You're reading it for nothing.

976
00:38:20,090 --> 00:38:22,300
That's why I called you here.

977
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:24,000
What does this say?

978
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:28,070
You'll have to beg me.

979
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:30,830
Forget it.

980
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:32,630
I'm not investigating the case anyway.

981
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:34,080
I might as well leave

982
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,660
and save the rest of the case

983
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,500
for Su Jiu'er

984
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,850
to worry about by herself.

985
00:38:37,850 --> 00:38:38,780
Don't.

986
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:40,660
I'll tell you.

987
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:41,370
I'll tell you.

988
00:38:41,370 --> 00:38:42,140
He hasn't made himself clear

989
00:38:42,140 --> 00:38:43,600
about what happened to Hu.

990
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:45,010
How could I let him go?

991
00:38:45,010 --> 00:38:46,550
You're investigating the Peony Case right now,

992
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,550
and you need help.

993
00:38:48,070 --> 00:38:49,500
We understand if you did this

994
00:38:49,500 --> 00:38:50,380
impulsively.

995
00:38:50,420 --> 00:38:51,380
Yes.

996
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:53,840
Since we're all on the same side here,

997
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:54,780
we can cover it up for you.

998
00:38:54,780 --> 00:38:55,710
Just admit to it.

999
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:57,100
You...

1000
00:39:01,050 --> 00:39:01,510
This...

1001
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:06,320
Commander Yan,

1002
00:39:06,680 --> 00:39:07,700
I really dont know

1003
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:09,630
how Han Zheng escaped from prison.

1004
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,100
If you

1005
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,430
still don't believe me,

1006
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:14,250
you can report it to the Law Department

1007
00:39:14,250 --> 00:39:15,510
and let them handle it.

1008
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:16,810
Commander,

1009
00:39:17,270 --> 00:39:18,820
I don't think that's appropriate.

1010
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:19,370
It's not.

1011
00:39:19,990 --> 00:39:21,370
As one of our patrols,

1012
00:39:21,410 --> 00:39:22,790
Prince Han

1013
00:39:22,810 --> 00:39:23,870
has already gotten someone killed.

1014
00:39:23,870 --> 00:39:24,750
Hu

1015
00:39:26,410 --> 00:39:27,050
Forget it.

1016
00:39:27,460 --> 00:39:28,990
Anyway, that's in the past.

1017
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:30,440
Now, he's gone missing.

1018
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,900
If we report it to the higher-ups,

1019
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,700
how humiliating would it be

1020
00:39:33,730 --> 00:39:34,670
for the Inspection Bureau?

1021
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,030
It'll be devastating,

1022
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:37,170
Commander Yan.

1023
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,230
Su Jiu'er.

1024
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:43,440
Hand me your badge.

1025
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:44,530
What?

1026
00:39:45,060 --> 00:39:46,520
You are suspended. Go home

1027
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:48,210
and wait for your punishment.

1028
00:39:48,210 --> 00:39:48,780
If we can't find Han Zheng

1029
00:39:48,780 --> 00:39:49,840
within three days,

1030
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:52,460
we will report it to the Law Department.

1031
00:40:05,100 --> 00:40:06,630
Jiu'er has been suspended?

1032
00:40:07,370 --> 00:40:08,440
Why don't you go out now

1033
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,170
and tell them

1034
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:11,290
-it wasn't Jiu'er who did it?
-Let go.

1035
00:40:11,350 --> 00:40:11,990
Let go!

1036
00:40:13,660 --> 00:40:14,790
What I'm holding now

1037
00:40:14,930 --> 00:40:16,140
is important evidence.

1038
00:40:16,140 --> 00:40:16,930
Why are you still talking about evidence

1039
00:40:16,930 --> 00:40:17,930
at this juncture?

1040
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:20,880
The flower on this hairpin is a moutan,

1041
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:21,880
not a peony.

1042
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:22,680
Yes.

1043
00:40:24,140 --> 00:40:25,600
Don't change the subject.

1044
00:40:25,660 --> 00:40:26,260
Boss,

1045
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:27,950
I don't understand.

1046
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:29,500
Didn't you say

1047
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:30,770
we should treat Jiu'er better?

1048
00:40:30,770 --> 00:40:31,850
Why did you suddenly...

1049
00:40:31,850 --> 00:40:32,510
-I...
-I...

1050
00:40:34,070 --> 00:40:35,400
I just couldn't help it.

1051
00:40:36,350 --> 00:40:37,490
When Hu left,

1052
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:38,730
she looked very sad.

1053
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:40,170
But now that she's alive and kicking

1054
00:40:40,170 --> 00:40:41,370
and working cases...

1055
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,730
I'm used to treating her like this.

1056
00:40:43,820 --> 00:40:44,340
Got it.

1057
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:44,910
Got it.

1058
00:40:45,700 --> 00:40:46,230
It's perfect timing.

1059
00:40:46,230 --> 00:40:47,290
Go and tell him now.

1060
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:48,590
Go with me right now.

1061
00:40:49,420 --> 00:40:50,420
Someone is there.

1062
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:00,160
Did you hear that?

1063
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,500
Where is he?

1064
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,810
He's not at home,

1065
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:24,110
and he's not at Qiwei Pavilion.

1066
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:25,740
He's not with Jun either.

1067
00:41:25,890 --> 00:41:27,300
Where exactly did he go?

1068
00:41:34,500 --> 00:41:35,020
Mother.

1069
00:41:36,140 --> 00:41:36,820
I'm back.

1070
00:41:41,700 --> 00:41:42,430
You're back?

1071
00:41:45,250 --> 00:41:46,010
Han Zheng?

1072
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,180
You're here?

1073
00:41:49,340 --> 00:41:50,940
How dare you come to my house?

1074
00:41:51,100 --> 00:41:51,630
Let's go.

1075
00:41:51,790 --> 00:41:52,540
Come with me to the Inspection Bureau.

1076
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:54,020
-Listen to me... -Jiu'er, youre back?

1077
00:41:54,020 --> 00:41:54,580
Jiu'er.

1078
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:57,130
The food is ready. It's time to eat.

1079
00:41:59,140 --> 00:41:59,600
Mother.

1080
00:42:00,090 --> 00:42:00,750
Did you know

1081
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,210
he escaped from prison?

1082
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:04,060
The Inspection Bureau thought I was the one who let him go.

1083
00:42:04,060 --> 00:42:05,570
They've even suspended me.

1084
00:42:05,570 --> 00:42:06,780
Isn't that good?

1085
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,850
I told you, that job of yours

1086
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,670
pays badly, works you too hard,

1087
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:11,390
and puts you in danger.

1088
00:42:11,390 --> 00:42:12,710
You're better off without it.

1089
00:42:12,710 --> 00:42:14,230
Mother, what's wrong with you?

1090
00:42:14,230 --> 00:42:15,380
He's Han Zheng.

1091
00:42:16,350 --> 00:42:17,950
Have you forgotten about Hu?

1092
00:42:18,230 --> 00:42:19,850
How could you let him into our house?

1093
00:42:19,850 --> 00:42:21,650
Jiu'er, I have something to say.

1094
00:42:22,970 --> 00:42:24,230
What do you have to say?

1095
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,480
I thought about it

1096
00:42:26,790 --> 00:42:27,920
over and over again.

1097
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:29,690
I finally remember now.

1098
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,950
I can be sure that on that day,

1099
00:42:32,020 --> 00:42:33,660
when I left the courtyard of the Western Chamber

1100
00:42:33,660 --> 00:42:34,520
with Keyuncha,

1101
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,120
Hu said to me,

1102
00:42:36,990 --> 00:42:38,620
"Han, you're befuddled."
